{
 "name": "RPlog_Masquerade_Ball_A_Night_on_Yavin_Part_1",
 "title": "Masquerade Ball: A Night on Yavin (Part 1)",
 "summary": "Aboard the entertainment ship Angry Rancor, the Jordain sisters Inanna and Sel host a tropical-themed masquerade ball above Yavin IV. Costumed guests filter into the lounge: Inanna dressed as a spotted cat oversees the bar, her sister Sel performs as a glittering golden 'Birdie' on stage, and Ka'una prowls about as a striped wildcat. A guest in an elaborate papier-mache totem head introduces himself as the spirit Ramyxth, while Maethor totters in as a walking tiki lamp and Solon Halwinder appears as an invisible Duke. Over flowing drinks, song, and dancing, the partygoers banter and tease one another into the costume revelry, with the reluctant Inanna finally coaxed onto the dance floor by Ramyxth.",
